'''尼古拉·布羅克-馬德森'''（{{lang-da|Nicolai Brock-Madsen}}；{{bd|1993年|1月8日}}）是一位[[丹麥|丹麥]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是前鋒，現效力[[丹麥足球超級聯賽|丹麥足球超級聯賽]]球會[[霍尔森斯联合俱乐部|霍尔森斯]]。他曾代表丹麥國家足球青年隊參賽。

==球會生涯==
===蘭訥斯===
布羅克-馬德森在家鄉的[[兰讷斯弗雷亚足球俱乐部|兰讷斯弗雷亚]]球會展開足球生涯，首顆職業進球是2010年[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧足联欧洲联赛]]對[[迪德朗日足球俱樂部|迪德朗日]]時取得，以6-1大勝對手<ref name=RandersFC>{{cite web |url=http://www.randersfc.dk/index.php?menu=47&side=spiller&spiller=117 |title=Førsteholdet 2014/2015 – Nicolai Brock-Madsen |language=da |trans-title=First team 2014/2015 – Nicolai Brock-Madsen |publisher=Randers FC |accessdate=2015-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924084725/http://www.randersfc.dk/index.php?menu=47&side=spiller&spiller=117 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012/13球季，他成為了球會的主力成員，共上場28次，並在[[丹麥盃|丹麥盃]]中打入決賽，可惜以1-0不敵[[埃斯比约联合足球俱乐部|埃斯比约]]無緣冠軍。

===伯明翰城===
2015年8月21日，布羅克-馬德森加盟英冠球會[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]，轉會費沒有對外公佈<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/nicolai-brock-madsen-birmingham-city-2635068.aspx |title=Blues sign highly-rated Danish striker Nicolai Brock-Madsen |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=2015-08-21 |accessdate=2015-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923213701/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/nicolai-brock-madsen-birmingham-city-2635068.aspx |archive-date=2015-09-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但[[BBC|BBC]]報導稱在50萬英鎊左右，按條件可增至100萬鎊<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34018385 |title=Birmingham City: Nicolai Brock-Madsen signs for Blues |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2015-08-21 |accessdate=2015-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822082934/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34018385 |archive-date=2015-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。四天後首次代表該球會上場，在下半場換入，球隊最終以2-0擊敗[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|吉林汉姆]]晉級[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第三輪<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/updated-birmingham-city-2-gillingham-9928262 |title=Updated: Birmingham City 2 Gillingham 0 |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2015-08-25 |accessdate=2015-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828011844/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/updated-birmingham-city-2-gillingham-9928262 |archive-date=2015-08-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月15日，他首次代表球隊在聯賽上場，以替補身入入替[[克莱顿·唐纳德森|克莱顿·唐纳德森]]，但仍無助球隊以1-0敗給[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-0-nottingham-forest-10064590 |title=Birmingham City 0 Nottingham Forest 1 |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2015-09-15 |accessdate=2015-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924074435/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-0-nottingham-forest-10064590 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

11月21日主場對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查尔顿]]的賽事，布羅克-馬德森首次先發上場，代替因國家隊受傷的克莱顿·唐纳德森出任單箭頭，球隊最終以1-0戰敗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-v-charlton-live-10474557 |title=Birmingham City v Charlton: live coverage |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2015-11-21 |accessdate=2015-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122172134/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-v-charlton-live-10474557 |archive-date=2015-11-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34816935 |title=Birmingham 0–1 Charlton |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2015-11-21 |accessdate=2015-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123100454/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34816935 |archive-date=2015-11-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。接下兩場賽事他仍然先發上場，可是輪到他受傷，他的位置被借用球員[[詹姆斯·沃根|-{zh-hans:詹姆斯·沃根; zh-hant:占士·禾根;}-]]取代。唐纳德森傷愈後回到先發位置，使布羅克-馬德森在餘下賽事均沒有上場機會<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-team-news-gary-10584323 |title=Birmingham City team news: Gary Rowett reveals that midfielder and striker are doubts for trip to Middlesbrough |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2015-12-11 |accessdate=2016-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813022946/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-team-news-gary-10584323 |archive-date=2016-08-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=sb1516>{{soccerbase season|65435|2015|accessdate=2016-05-26}}</ref>。

由於需要參加[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會]]，使布羅克-馬德森錯過球隊的季前集訓和季初比賽。在轉會窗最後一天，他被外借至荷蘭球會[[PEC施禾利|PEC施禾利]]至季末<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-citys-nicolai-brock-madsen-11826571 |title=Birmingham City's Nicolai Brock-Madsen seals deadline day move |first=Mat |last=Kendrick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2016-08-31 |accessdate=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160831203758/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-citys-nicolai-brock-madsen-11826571 |archive-date=2016-08-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，據報導該球會有購入條款<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.peczwolle.nl/nl/laatste-nieuws_1/nicolai-brock-madsen-naar-pec-zwolle2016-08-31 |title=Nicolai Brock-Madsen naar PEC Zwolle |language=nl |trans-title=Nicolai Brock-Madsen to PEC Zwolle |publisher=PEC Zwolle |date=2016-08-31 |accessdate=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916235753/http://www.peczwolle.nl/nl/laatste-nieuws_1/nicolai-brock-madsen-naar-pec-zwolle2016-08-31 |archive-date=2016-09-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。加盟後便立即
代表球會在[[荷兰足球甲级联赛|荷兰足球甲级联赛]]首次上場，9月10日以先發身份上場參加對[[烏德勒支足球會|烏德勒支]]。之後的[[荷蘭盃|荷蘭盃]]第一輪對第四級球會[[DVS'33足球會|DVS'33]]梅開二度，以4-1取勝。布羅克-馬德森在上季受到傷患困擾，但冬歇後他保持出色狀態，在六場比賽中打進五球<ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/08/13/world/olympics/nigeria-under-23/denmark-u23/2167942/ |title=Nigeria U23 vs. Denmark U23 2–0 |website=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827105440/http://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/08/13/world/olympics/nigeria-under-23/denmark-u23/2167942/ |archive-date=2016-08-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整個球季，他在各項賽事上場25次並打進10球。儘管PEC施禾利希望留住布羅克-馬德森<ref name=StayZwolle/>，但據報導他本人希望回到伯明翰在新教練[[哈里·雷德克纳普|-{zh-hans:哈里·雷德克纳普; zh-hant:哈利·列納;}-]]取得一席位<ref name=StayZwolle>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/pec-zwolle-technical-director-hopes-12853662 |title=PEC Zwolle technical director on his hopes for the future of Birmingham City striker Nicolai Brock-Madsen |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-04-06 |accessdate=2017-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826120706/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/pec-zwolle-technical-director-hopes-12853662 |archive-date=2017-08-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-city-comment-nicolai-brock-13144912 |title=Birmingham City comment: Nicolai Brock-Madsen will undoubtedly have learned from a season in the Eredivisie |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-06-06 |accessdate=2017-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706102230/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-city-comment-nicolai-brock-13144912 |archive-date=2017-07-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，可是雷德克纳普明確表示他本人在伯明翰並沒有未來。布羅克-馬德森自由轉會至荷蘭球會的交易告吹<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-transfer-news-harry-13436486 |title=Birmingham City transfer news: Harry Redknapp's blunt verdict on the future of Nicolai Brock-Madsen |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-08-05 |accessdate=2018-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180119120054/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-transfer-news-harry-13436486 |archive-date=2018-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，布羅克-馬德森本人亦拒絕了丹麥球會的邀請。雷德克纳普的繼任者[[史蒂夫·科特里爾|史蒂夫·科特里爾]]即使在球隊前鋒無力的情況下，亦不起用布羅克-馬德森<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-city-transfer-brock-madsen-14053601 |title=Transfer news: Birmingham City's plan for forgotten man revealed |first=Alex |last=Dicken |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2018-01-05 |accessdate=2018-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180119002745/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-city-transfer-brock-madsen-14053601 |archive-date=2018-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===克拉科維亞===
2018年1月18日，不被重用的布羅克-馬德森被外借至[[波蘭足球甲級聯賽|波蘭足球甲級聯賽]]球會[[克拉科維亞足球俱樂部|克拉科維亞]]至季末，亦附有購買權<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2018/nicolai-brock-madsen-loaned-to-ks-cracovia/ |title=Nicolai Brock-Madsen loaned to KS Cracovia |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=2018-01-18 |accessdate=2018-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180119001158/https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2018/nicolai-brock-madsen-loaned-to-ks-cracovia/ |archive-date=2018-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。波蘭冬歇復賽後的2月10日對[[弗羅茨瓦夫足球俱樂部|弗羅茨瓦夫]]的比賽，他在下半場入替上場，最終以2-1全取3分。整個外借期間他共上場11次及打進1球。

===聖美倫===
布羅克-馬德森在2018年8月被外借至[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會[[圣米伦足球俱乐部|圣米伦]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/45131557 |title=Nicolai Brock-Madsen: St Mirren sign Birmingham striker on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2018-08-09 |accessdate=2018-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180809122007/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/45131557 |archive-date=2018-08-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在同月11日客訪[[格拉斯哥流浪足球會|格拉斯哥流浪]]時先發上場，比賽至69分鐘被換下<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/rangers-vs-st-mirren-live-13058513 |title=Rangers 2 St Mirren 0 Recap: Steven Gerrard's men take all three points despite red card |first1=Mark |last1=McDougall |first2=Stuart |last2=Hodge |newspaper=Daily Record |location=Glasgow |date=2018-08-12 |accessdate=2018-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180812213045/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/rangers-vs-st-mirren-live-13058513 |archive-date=2018-08-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。上場5次未取得入球後，球隊新教練[[奧兰·卡尼|奧兰·卡尼]]向布羅克-馬德森表示他在自己的計劃內。布羅克-馬德森於10月中回到伯明翰操練，但因仍屬外借身份在2019年1月1日前不能代表伯明翰比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/45873749 |title=Birmingham City's Nicolai Brock-Madsen leaves St Mirren after five games |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2018-10-16 |accessdate=2019-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181111034039/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/45873749 |archive-date=2018-11-11 |dead-url=no }}<br>{{cite web |url=https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2018/nicolai-brock-madsen-back-at-blues/ |title=Nicolai Brock-Madsen back at Blues |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=2018-10-19 |accessdate=2019-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181020224035/https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2018/nicolai-brock-madsen-back-at-blues/ |archive-date=2018-10-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雙方於2019年元旦解除合約<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2018/nicolai-brock-madsen-departs-blues/ |title=Nicolai Brock-Madsen departs Blues |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=2018-12-17 |accessdate=2019-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218010759/https://www.bcfc.com/news/articles/2018/nicolai-brock-madsen-departs-blues/ |archive-date=2018-12-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===賀森斯===
2019年1月21日，他與丹超球會[[霍尔森斯联合俱乐部|霍尔森斯]]簽下6個月短期合約<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.tipsbladet.dk/nyhed/superliga/ac-horsens-henter-nicolai-brock-madsen-hjem-til-danmark |title=AC Horsens henter Nicolai Brock-Madsen hjem til Danmark |publisher=Tipsbladet |date=2019-01-21 |accessdate=2019-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190121182513/https://www.tipsbladet.dk/nyhed/superliga/ac-horsens-henter-nicolai-brock-madsen-hjem-til-danmark |archive-date=2019-01-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
布羅克-馬德森曾代表[[丹麥18歲以下國家足球隊|丹麥U18]]至[[丹麥21歲以下國家足球隊|U21]]各階級青年隊上場<ref name=DBUprofile>{{cite web |url=http://www.dbu.dk/landshold/Landsholdsdatabasen/LBaseplayerInfo.aspx?playerid=6869 |title=Landshold: Nicolai Brock-Madsen |language=da |trans-title=International team: Nicolai Brock-Madsen |publisher=Dansk Boldspil-Union |accessdate=2015-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923230320/http://www.dbu.dk/landshold/Landsholdsdatabasen/LBaseplayerInfo.aspx?playerid=6869 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年6月，他被[[丹麥21歲以下國家足球隊|丹麥奧運隊]]徵召參加奧運前三場熱身賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dbu.dk/Nyheder/2016/Maj/Trup_final_Sydkorea |title=Sidste spillere på plads til Sydkorea |language=da |trans-title=Last players in place for South Korea |first=Pia |last=Schou Nielsen |publisher=Dansk Boldspil-Union |date=2016-05-25 |accessdate=2016-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527233434/http://www.dbu.dk/Nyheder/2016/Maj/Trup_final_Sydkorea |archive-date=2016-05-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外他亦出戰[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會男子足球比賽|奧運]]小組賽三場比賽，但未有進球<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=395446/index.html |title=Nicolai Brock-Madsen |publisher=FIFA |accessdate=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915134959/http://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=395446/index.html |archive-date=2016-09-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，丹麥最終以第二名完成小組賽。可是他沒有在淘汰賽第一輪不敵[[尼日利亞23歲以下國家足球隊|尼日利亞]]一戰上場<ref name="#1"/>。

